{
  "_about": "Golden fixture \u2014 a clean, fully-tokenized 3-component / 3-screen dogfood project. CI renders this twice and asserts byte-identical output, checks render-time budget, and runs check.py --strict (must be CLEAN: no raw hex/px in render bodies, every orgId resolves, danger token present). e2e_smoke.py boots it through serve.py. Keep it token-only \u2014 it is the reference for Principle 2 (token-only styling).",
